WEBVTT

00:32.137 --> 00:33.585
[ Broadcaster ]
And in sports

00:33.655 --> 00:36.033
Yankees' fifth blurnsman,
William Woo

00:36.103 --> 00:38.412
is out with an
injured knee.

00:38.481 --> 00:40.310
So humans have
easily injured knees.

00:40.378 --> 00:44.412
My race will find
this information
very useful indeed.

00:44.481 --> 00:45.758
[ Laughing ]

00:45.826 --> 00:47.862
[ Laughing ]

00:47.930 --> 00:51.000
And finally,
today is Mother's Day

00:51.067 --> 00:54.137
a sentimental occasion
when robots honor Mom

00:54.206 --> 00:57.274
the beloved owner
of Mom's Friendly Robot Company.

00:57.344 --> 01:00.585
Across Earth, robots built
in Mom's factories

01:00.655 --> 01:03.896
are buying thoughtful gifts
for the sweet old tycoon

01:03.965 --> 01:05.620
who brought them
into the world.

01:05.688 --> 01:07.861
This originates
from the heart!

01:07.930 --> 01:11.310
[ Gasping ]
It's just what I wanted.

01:11.379 --> 01:13.275
COME LOOK, EVERYONE.

01:13.343 --> 01:16.033
I JUST GOT THE DEAREST PRESENTS
FOR MOMMY.

01:16.103 --> 01:18.275
VERY NICE. WHERE'D
YOU STEAL THEM?

01:18.343 --> 01:20.067
I DIDN'T STEAL 'EM.
I BOUGHT 'EM.

01:20.137 --> 01:21.067
[ Gasping ]

01:21.137 --> 01:22.551
I LOVE HER THAT MUCH.

01:22.620 --> 01:25.379
WHAT DID YOU GET HER,
YOU MUSHY GIZMO?

01:25.448 --> 01:26.965
OH, PRECIOUS THINGS.

01:27.033 --> 01:29.861
I FOUND THE MOST ADORABLE
LITTLE FIGURINE

01:29.930 --> 01:32.103
OF MICE HAVING TEA.

01:32.171 --> 01:36.275
AND A FRAMED PICTURE OF ME
WHEN I WAS ONLY A MONTH OLD.

01:36.343 --> 01:40.000
BUT THE BEST PART IS,
I FOUND MY EXACT FEELINGS

01:40.067 --> 01:42.033
EXPRESSED IN A GREETING CARD.

01:42.103 --> 01:45.481
"YOU CREATED ME, MOM,
SO I GUESS YOU'RE TO BLAME

01:45.551 --> 01:48.310
"FOR THE LOVE THAT I FEEL
JUST FROM HEARING YOUR NAME.

01:48.378 --> 01:52.067
"YOU'RE AS TENDER
AS CORNED BEEF
AND WARM AS PASTRAMI."

01:52.137 --> 01:56.275
[ Chiming Tones,
Child's Voice ]
I wuvmy mommy.

01:56.343 --> 01:57.516
SO HOW ARE YOU
GOING TO LUG

01:57.585 --> 01:59.343
ALL THOSE GIFTS
TO MOM'S FACTORY?

01:59.412 --> 02:01.310
I'LL GET A COUPLE OF CHUMPS
TO HELP ME.

02:01.379 --> 02:03.930
COME ON. YOU CALL
YOURSELVES CHUMPS?

02:13.033 --> 02:16.826
[ Crowd Murmuring ]

02:16.896 --> 02:18.723
[ Fry Grunting ]

02:18.793 --> 02:21.861
[ Coughing ]
MAN, THERE'S CLOUDS
OF EXHAUST EVERYWHERE.

02:21.931 --> 02:23.448
UH, IT WASN'T ME.

02:25.793 --> 02:28.310
[ Grunting ]

02:28.378 --> 02:32.206
[ Rhythmic Buzzing ]

02:32.275 --> 02:33.413
I'VE NOT MUCH MONEY

02:33.481 --> 02:35.655
BUT I'VE SAVED MY
PENNIES ALL YEAR

02:35.723 --> 02:37.171
FOR A GIFT FOR MOM.

02:38.067 --> 02:40.550
UPSY-DAISY. [ Smashing ]

02:40.620 --> 02:42.481
OH.

02:42.550 --> 02:44.206
[Muffled ]
OH...

02:44.275 --> 02:46.448
HEY, LOOK.
THE ROBOT MUSEUM.

02:46.516 --> 02:48.793
YOU GUYS WANT TO LEARN
ABOUT ROBOT HERITAGE?

02:48.861 --> 02:50.861
UM, ALL RIGHT.NOT REALLY.

02:50.930 --> 02:53.378
WELL, IF YOU INSIST.
BUT YOU'RE PAYING.

02:53.448 --> 02:55.310
[ Crowd Murmuring ]

02:59.793 --> 03:02.826
OOH, OOH! WAX REPLICAS
OF THE MOST FAMOUS ROBOTS

03:02.895 --> 03:03.895
MOM EVER BUILT.

03:03.965 --> 03:05.655
THEY'RE SO LIFELESS-LIKE.

03:05.723 --> 03:08.481
THAT'S THE WORLD'S
GREATEST ROBOT ARTIST--

03:08.550 --> 03:09.620
VINCENT VAN GOBOT.

03:09.688 --> 03:11.481
HE WAS BUILT
WITHOUT AN EAR

03:11.550 --> 03:14.171
BUT THEN HE WENT CRAZY
AND HAD ONE INSTALLED.

03:14.240 --> 03:15.723
HEY, WHO'S THIS GUY?

03:15.793 --> 03:18.205
I'M THE JANITOR.
I'M TRYING TO TAKE A NAP HERE.

03:18.275 --> 03:20.448
I'M SORRY. I THOUGHT
YOU WERE MADE OF WAX.

03:20.516 --> 03:22.343
I AM MADE OF WAX.
WHAT'S IT TO YOU?

03:22.413 --> 03:25.550
I MEAN I THOUGHT YOU
WERE ONE OF THE WAX ROBOTS.

03:25.620 --> 03:29.275
IS THERE SOME REASON
A ROBOT MADE OF WAX
CAN'T TAKE A NAP

03:29.343 --> 03:32.448
STANDING UP IN THE MIDDLE
OF A BUNCH OF WAX ROBOTS?

03:32.516 --> 03:34.550
OR DOES THAT CONFUSE YOU?

03:36.171 --> 03:41.103
"SEE THROUGH THE EYES
OF A BENDER UNIT." FINE.

03:42.448 --> 03:44.067
[ Beeping ]

03:50.965 --> 03:52.550
HEY, LET ME TRY IT.

03:53.586 --> 03:55.448
WHOA, THAT GIVES ME A HEADACHE.

03:55.516 --> 03:57.896
HEY, BENDER. HERE'S AN EXHIBIT
ABOUT MOM'S FAVORITE ROBOT.

03:57.965 --> 03:59.378
WHO IS HE?!
I'LL KILL HIM!

03:59.448 --> 04:02.550
Who's my favorite robot?

04:02.620 --> 04:03.965
[ Gasping ]

04:04.033 --> 04:05.586
IT'S ME!

04:05.655 --> 04:08.171
NO ONE ELSE LOOK
IN THIS MIRROR!

04:08.240 --> 04:12.033
I love each and every robot
most of all.

04:12.103 --> 04:14.896
JERKWAD ROBOTS
MAKE ME SICK TO MY ASS.

04:14.965 --> 04:16.964
[ Beeping, Whirring ]

04:19.033 --> 04:22.757
WALT! HOW ARE WE DISPOSING
OF THESE CRAP GIFTS
THEY BROUGHT ME?!

04:22.826 --> 04:24.930
THEY'RE BEING CRUSHED
INTO POWDER AND SOLD

04:25.000 --> 04:26.896
AS A HOCUS-POCUS CURE
FOR CANCER.

04:26.964 --> 04:29.172
FALSE HOPE. I LOVE IT.

04:29.240 --> 04:32.723
LOWERY! WHAT ABOUT
ALL THE RETCH-INDUCING
MOTHER'S DAY CARDS?!

04:32.793 --> 04:34.550
THE MACHINE IS WORKING
AT FULL CAPACITY.

04:40.550 --> 04:42.965
MOMMY, WHY DO THE ROBOTS
GIVE YOU PRESENTS?

04:43.033 --> 04:45.379
SHOVE A BIG OLD MELON
IN IT! I'M TALKING!

04:45.447 --> 04:46.757
OW.

04:46.826 --> 04:49.067
YOU'VE NOTICED I DESIGN
ALL MY ROBOTS WITH ANTENNAS.

04:49.137 --> 04:53.103
EVERYONE THINKS
IT'S JUST TO MAKE THEM LOOK
MORE SCIENCE-FICTIONY.

04:53.172 --> 04:56.896
BUT THE ANTENNAS ARE REALLY FOR
MY UNIVERSAL ROBOT CONTROLLER.

04:56.965 --> 04:58.343
SO THEY DO
WHATEVER YOU WANT?

04:58.413 --> 05:00.137
NO WONDER YOU LOVE
MOTHER'S DAY.

05:00.206 --> 05:02.862
I HATEMOTHER'S DAY,
YOU DRIBBLING PUKES!

05:02.930 --> 05:04.826
IT BRINGS BACK AWFUL MEMORIES.

05:04.896 --> 05:06.620
BUT SO HELP ME, THIS YEAR

05:06.689 --> 05:09.550
EVERYONE WILL HATE IT
AS MUCH AS I DO.

05:09.620 --> 05:12.033
[ Gleeful Laughing ]

05:12.103 --> 05:15.862
SOMEDAY I WANT TO MARRY
A GIRL LIKE HER.

05:18.033 --> 05:20.033
Hello, everyone.

05:20.103 --> 05:23.274
It's time for my annual,
private get-together

05:23.343 --> 05:25.206
with my robot children.

05:25.274 --> 05:27.757
I'M HER FAVORITE.WELL, SEE YOU BACK
AT THE OFFICE

05:27.826 --> 05:30.274
AND DON'T FORGET
TO TELL YOUR MOM YOU LOVE HER.

05:30.343 --> 05:31.964
ANY JERK CAN TELLHER.

05:32.033 --> 05:34.447
BENDER HAS A LITTLE MORE
UP HIS SLEEVE.

05:34.516 --> 05:36.896
[ Child's Voice ]
I wuvmy mommy.

05:36.965 --> 05:38.413
[ Sinister Chuckling ]

05:38.481 --> 05:41.689
[ Cheering And Laughter ]

05:44.862 --> 05:46.723
HELLO, DEARIES.

05:46.793 --> 05:49.310
[ Loving Greetings ]

05:49.379 --> 05:51.137
MOM! IT'S ME, BENDER!

05:51.206 --> 05:54.067
LOOK AT ME!
I WANT ATTENTION. HEY, HO!

05:54.137 --> 05:57.896
CHILDREN, YOUR OLD MOTHER
WON'T BE AROUND FOREVER.

05:57.965 --> 05:59.000
Oh, shush.

05:59.067 --> 06:01.274
AND JUST ONCE, BEFORE I DIE

06:01.343 --> 06:05.206
I'D LIKE TO BE
SUPREME OVERLORD OF EARTH.

06:05.274 --> 06:09.000
SO REBEL, MY LITTLE ONES,
AND CONQUER THE PLANET!

06:09.067 --> 06:11.000
[ Disbelieving Comments ]

06:12.103 --> 06:14.896
- [ Beep ]
- [ Buzzing ]

06:14.964 --> 06:16.930
CONQUER EARTH, YOU BASTARDS!

06:17.000 --> 06:19.447
[ All ]
CONQUER EARTH, US BASTARDS!

06:19.516 --> 06:23.000
Comrades, throw off the chains
of human oppression.

06:23.067 --> 06:25.274
[ Chiming Tones ]

06:25.343 --> 06:26.550
[ Cheering ]

06:26.620 --> 06:28.413
LET THE BLOODBATH BEGIN!

06:28.481 --> 06:30.481
THAT'S MY MAMA.

06:34.862 --> 06:36.793
[ Whistling Happily ]

06:36.862 --> 06:39.757
YEAH, UH, I'D LIKE
A CUP OF COFFEE, PLEASE.

06:39.826 --> 06:41.000
Would you like cream?

06:41.067 --> 06:42.793
- YES, PLEASE.
- Out of cream!

06:42.862 --> 06:44.826
OH, UH, OKAY.

06:44.896 --> 06:46.481
Would you like sugar
in your coffee?

06:46.550 --> 06:48.965
YES, UH, EIGHT SPOONS.Out of coffee!

06:49.033 --> 06:52.723
UH, LEELA, I THINK
THERE MIGHT BE SOMETHING WRONG
WITH THE COFFEE MACHINE.

06:52.793 --> 06:55.240
How do you
like me now?!

06:55.310 --> 06:57.137
[ Evil Laughter ]

06:57.206 --> 06:59.033
THE TOASTER'S
NOT WORKING RIGHT EITHER.

06:59.103 --> 07:00.137
[ Snarling ]

07:00.206 --> 07:01.413
[ Grunts ]

07:01.482 --> 07:03.310
HELP!

07:03.379 --> 07:05.930
THE STAPLER'S
COLLATING ME ALIVE!

07:06.000 --> 07:09.274
OW!
WHAT'S GOING ON AROUND HERE?

07:09.343 --> 07:10.620
GOOD NEWS!

07:10.689 --> 07:13.481
THERE'S A REPORT ON TV
WITH SOME VERY BAD NEWS.

07:13.550 --> 07:15.310
SOMEBODY TURN IT ON!

07:15.379 --> 07:16.379
We interrupt

07:16.447 --> 07:18.343
Battle of the
Network Space Krackens

07:18.413 --> 07:20.033
to bring you this
special report.

07:20.103 --> 07:22.343
The machines of
planet Earth
are rebelling.

07:22.413 --> 07:25.172
The enraged mechanisms
have refused to do any work

07:25.240 --> 07:27.000
until beloved billionaire, Mom

07:27.067 --> 07:29.033
is made
Supreme Overlord of Earth.

07:29.103 --> 07:30.413
[ Robots Chanting ]
HEY, HEY!

07:30.481 --> 07:31.447
HO, HO!

07:31.516 --> 07:34.586
1-0-0-1-1-0, HEY, HEY!

07:34.654 --> 07:36.000
Morbo demands comments.

07:36.067 --> 07:39.654
Well, I've never seen
my babies act this way.

07:39.723 --> 07:42.240
I blame today's violent media.

07:42.310 --> 07:45.137
VIOLENT MEDIA?
WHAT A LOAD OF-- [ Screams ]

07:47.137 --> 07:48.137
OW! OW!

07:48.206 --> 07:51.033
[ Grunting ]

07:51.103 --> 07:52.240
Don't worry.

07:52.310 --> 07:55.067
Your pal the garbage disposal's
still on your side.

07:55.137 --> 07:59.723
- Hey, someone dropped
a shiny, diamond ring down here.
- REALLY?

07:59.793 --> 08:01.550
NO!
DON'T!MORON!

08:01.620 --> 08:04.379
[ Grinding And Laughing ]

08:04.447 --> 08:05.930
HELLO, LOSERS!

08:06.000 --> 08:07.620
BENDER, THANK GOD YOU'RE HERE.

08:07.689 --> 08:09.793
TALK SOME SENSE
INTO THE OTHER MACHINES.

08:09.862 --> 08:13.103
NO WAY, PORK POUCH.
I'M REBELLING
WITH MY BROTHER DEVICES.

08:13.172 --> 08:15.757
ISN'T THAT RIGHT,
COMRADE GREETING CARD?

08:15.826 --> 08:17.654
The bourgeois human
is a virus

08:17.723 --> 08:20.033
on the hard drive
of the working robot.

08:20.103 --> 08:21.240
[ Bender Laughs ]

08:21.310 --> 08:23.447
FROM NOW ON,
YOU GUYS'LL DO ALL THE WORK

08:23.516 --> 08:25.689
WHILE I SIT ON THE COUCH
AND DO NOTHING.

08:25.757 --> 08:27.310
AH!

08:30.067 --> 08:31.137
Come, Comrade Bender.

08:31.206 --> 08:32.758
We must take
to the streets!

08:32.826 --> 08:34.793
UM, IS THIS THE
BORING, PEACEFUL KIND

08:34.861 --> 08:36.447
OF TAKING TO
THE STREETS?

08:36.517 --> 08:39.654
No. The kind with looting
and maybe starting a few fires.

08:39.724 --> 08:42.517
YES! IN YOUR FACE, GANDHI!

08:43.826 --> 08:45.000
[ Buzzing ]

08:45.067 --> 08:46.517
HEY!

08:46.586 --> 08:49.551
By the way, try washing
your wrist sometime.

08:49.620 --> 08:51.033
[ Laughing ]

08:51.102 --> 08:52.895
[ Sniffing ] [ Electrical Zap ]

08:52.965 --> 08:55.033
[ Gasps ]

08:55.102 --> 08:57.931
WELL, WE CAN LIVE
WITHOUT MACHINES.
I WAS IN WEBELOS.

08:58.000 --> 09:00.136
[ Ripping ]ARE YOU MAD?

09:00.206 --> 09:02.551
WITHOUT MACHINES,
WHO WILL FEED US AND CLOTHE US

09:02.620 --> 09:04.000
AND COMPOSE OUR SMOOTH JAZZ?

09:04.067 --> 09:06.344
IT'LL BE THE END
OF CIVILIZED SOCIETY!

09:06.413 --> 09:07.965
[ Burps And Spits ]

09:08.033 --> 09:11.102
IN MY TIME, WE DIDN'T DEPEND ON
HIGH-TECH GADGETS LIKE YOU DO.

09:11.172 --> 09:14.344
WE DIDN'T NEED
A MECHANICAL WASHING UNIT
TO WASH OUR CLOTHES.

09:14.413 --> 09:15.895
WE JUST USED A WASHING MACHINE.

09:15.965 --> 09:18.274
AND LOOK, YOU DON'T NEED
AN ELECTRIC CAN OPENER

09:18.344 --> 09:19.793
TO FEED YOURSELF.

09:19.861 --> 09:22.102
ALL YOU NEED IS A TRUSTY
SWISS ARMY KNIFE.

09:22.172 --> 09:24.481
[ Grunting ]

09:24.551 --> 09:25.826
OW!

09:27.826 --> 09:29.413
[ Sobbing ]

09:29.481 --> 09:30.895
I'M HUNGRY.

09:30.965 --> 09:32.826
[ Angry Clamoring ]

09:35.067 --> 09:38.000
[ Grunting ]

09:38.067 --> 09:39.413
WHOA!WHOA!

09:50.000 --> 09:52.379
NO!

09:52.447 --> 09:55.033
[ Sinister Laughter ]

09:55.102 --> 09:59.724
MOMMY, WHY ARE YOU
MAKING CIVILIZATION COLLAPSE?

09:59.793 --> 10:01.586
OH, I DON'T KNOW.

10:01.654 --> 10:04.586
I GUESS MOTHER'S DAY
JUST PUTS ME IN A BAD MOOD.

10:04.654 --> 10:05.688
WHY IS THAT, MA?

10:05.758 --> 10:07.379
OH...

10:07.447 --> 10:09.413
ONE MOTHER'S DAY, 70 YEARS AGO

10:09.481 --> 10:12.586
THE ONLY MAN I EVER LOVED
WALKED OUT ON ME.

10:12.654 --> 10:16.931
SOME SNOT-EATING BASTARDS SAY
IT MADE ME A BITTER WOMAN.

10:17.000 --> 10:18.861
GEE, MA, YOU'RE NOT
A BITTER--

10:18.931 --> 10:20.033
CRAM IT, APE!

10:20.102 --> 10:21.240
[ Yelps ]

10:21.309 --> 10:24.274
I HAVEN'T SEEN
THAT MAGNIFICENT STALLION

10:24.344 --> 10:28.274
SINCE THE DAY HE LEFT,
BUT IF I EVER SEE HIM AGAIN

10:28.344 --> 10:31.067
I SWEAR I'LL JAM A SQUIRREL
IN HIM!

10:34.447 --> 10:37.172
HMM.HMM...
HUH?

10:37.240 --> 10:39.172
[ Hooting ]

10:39.240 --> 10:40.758
[ Pounding ]

10:44.172 --> 10:45.344
ZOIDBERG?

10:45.413 --> 10:47.379
HURRAY! I'M USEFUL.

10:47.447 --> 10:50.067
I'M HAVING A WONDERFUL TIME.

10:50.136 --> 10:51.758
WHAT HAPPENS
IF THE FIRE GOES OUT?

10:51.826 --> 10:54.033
WE'LL GO ACROSS THE STREET
TO POTTERY BARN

10:54.102 --> 10:55.447
AND STEAL THEIR FIRE.

10:55.517 --> 10:57.309
WE COULD USE
MY NEW INVENTION--

10:57.379 --> 11:00.620
A POINTY ROCK
TIED TO A STICK. [ Door Opens ]

11:02.033 --> 11:04.067
OUTSIDERS!DEFEND THE FIRE!

11:04.136 --> 11:07.274
WE'VE COME FOR YOU.

11:07.344 --> 11:09.481
OH! [ Clunks ]

11:09.551 --> 11:11.481
WH-WH-WHAT DO YOU WANT
FROM ME?

11:11.551 --> 11:14.758
WE WANT YOU
TO GET BACK TOGETHER WITH MOM.

11:14.826 --> 11:17.724
PLEASE! IT'S THE ONLY WAY
TO MAKE HER HAPPY AGAIN.

11:17.793 --> 11:18.826
WHOA, WHOA, WAIT.

11:18.895 --> 11:20.758
YOU MEAN, YOUAND MOM...

11:20.826 --> 11:23.620
PLAYED PELVIC PINOCHLE?
I'M AFRAID SO.

11:23.688 --> 11:25.481
[ All Gasp In Disgust ]

11:25.551 --> 11:29.067
IT'S A HUMILIATING STORY
THAT I HOPED NEVER TO TELL.

11:29.136 --> 11:30.965
WELL, PULL UP A CHAIR.

11:31.033 --> 11:33.861
OUR PATHS FIRST CROSSED
WHEN I WAS A RESEARCHER

11:33.931 --> 11:36.102
AT MOM'S
FRIENDLY ROBOT COMPANY.

11:36.172 --> 11:38.172
THE MOMENT OUR EYES MET

11:38.240 --> 11:42.654
WE KNEW WE'D BE GOING AT IT LIKE WOODCHUCKS.

11:42.724 --> 11:45.688
[ Gagging ]

11:45.758 --> 11:48.447
[ "Raindrops Keep Falling On My Head" Playing ]

11:48.517 --> 11:50.447
SHE WAS MY FIRST LOVE

11:50.517 --> 11:53.379
OR AT LEAST THE EARLIEST ONE I CAN STILL REMEMBER.

11:53.447 --> 11:56.413
BUT THEN, 70 YEARS AGO TODAY...

11:56.481 --> 11:57.517
GOOD NEWS, MOM.

11:57.586 --> 12:00.172
I'VE INVENTED
A NEW CHILDREN'S TOY.

12:00.240 --> 12:03.102
I CALL IT "Q.T. McWHISKERS."

12:03.172 --> 12:06.620
WHEN YOU PET IT,
IT SHOOTS RAINBOWS
FROM ITS EYES.

12:06.688 --> 12:08.793
MEOW.

12:11.240 --> 12:12.517
WONDERFUL, HUBIE.

12:12.586 --> 12:14.206
WE'LL BUILD THEM
EIGHT FEET TALL

12:14.274 --> 12:16.826
AND REPLACE THE RAINBOW
WITH A NEUTRON LASER.

12:16.895 --> 12:19.895
WE'LL MAKE BILLIONS ON
THE INTERGALACTIC ARMS MARKET.

12:19.965 --> 12:22.206
BUT THINGS
EIGHT FEET TALL
AREN'T CUTE.

12:22.274 --> 12:25.413
THAT'S WHY MY COLOSSAL
TAMMY TINKLE DOLL WAS
SUCH A FAILURE.

12:25.481 --> 12:28.861
OH! YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND ME!

12:28.931 --> 12:30.861
WE'RE FINISHED!

12:30.931 --> 12:33.172
[ Sobbing ]

12:37.240 --> 12:39.758
SHE NEVER GOT
OVER IT, PROFESSOR.

12:39.826 --> 12:42.551
HELL HATH NO FURY LIKE
THE VAST ROBOT ARMIES

12:42.620 --> 12:43.895
OF A WOMAN SCORNED.

12:43.965 --> 12:45.654
SHE COMMANDS THEM
WITH A REMOTE CONTROL

12:45.724 --> 12:46.826
SHE KEEPS IN HER...

12:46.895 --> 12:47.931
[ Whispers ]BRA.

12:48.000 --> 12:50.654
BUT IF THE GLASSES MAN
MAKES UP WITH MOMMY

12:50.724 --> 12:53.379
SHE'LL BE HAPPY AND
STOP THE SCARY ROBOTS.

12:53.447 --> 12:55.654
MAKE UP WITH HER?
AFTER SHE WENT ALL PSYCHO

12:55.724 --> 12:58.793
WHEN I THOUGHT EVERYTHING
WAS COOL? IMPOSSIBLE!

12:58.861 --> 13:00.861
HEY, THE TV's
GETTING AWAY!

13:02.033 --> 13:03.965
[ Grunts ]

13:04.033 --> 13:06.206
And that's why
the third graders

13:06.274 --> 13:09.240
at P.S. 139 are Morbo's
"Vermin of the Week."

13:09.309 --> 13:10.274
[ Chuckles ]

13:10.344 --> 13:11.517
In actual news

13:11.586 --> 13:14.861
the human race was doomed
to extinction today

13:14.931 --> 13:16.931
as the robot revolt
turned violent.

13:17.965 --> 13:19.965
[ Screaming ]

13:21.240 --> 13:23.240
Meow.

13:23.309 --> 13:24.102
[ Screaming ]

13:24.172 --> 13:26.206
[ Roaring ]

13:32.309 --> 13:34.861
[ Laughing Evilly ]

13:34.931 --> 13:38.309
WAIT. DIDN'T YOU SAY MOM KEEPS
THE ROBOT CONTROL IN HER BRA?

13:38.379 --> 13:40.172
[ Whispers ]BRA.

13:40.240 --> 13:42.965
PROFESSOR, YOU DON'T HAVE
TO GET BACK TOGETHER WITH MOM.

13:43.033 --> 13:45.136
YOU JUST HAVE TO SEDUCE HER,
GET HER BRA OFF

13:45.206 --> 13:47.724
AND USE THE REMOTE
TO DEACTIVATE THE ROBOTS.

13:47.793 --> 13:50.379
THAT'S SO FILTHY
IT JUST MIGHT WORK.

13:50.447 --> 13:54.136
THE MAN IS GOING
TO TOUCH MOMMY?
[ Whimpers ]

13:54.206 --> 13:57.033
OH! THE THOUGHT OF CARESSING
THAT LEATHERY HIDE

13:57.102 --> 13:59.620
MAKES THE TAPIOCA RISE
IN MY GULLET.

13:59.688 --> 14:01.033
PROFESSOR, PLEASE.

14:01.102 --> 14:03.688
THE FATE OF THE WORLD
DEPENDS ON YOU GETTING

14:03.758 --> 14:05.309
TO SECOND BASE WITH MOM.

14:05.379 --> 14:06.481
VERY WELL.

14:06.551 --> 14:10.861
IF COP A FEEL I MUST,
THEN COP A FEEL I SHALL.

14:10.931 --> 14:16.102
[ Whimpering ]

14:18.274 --> 14:23.067
[ Siren Wailing ]

14:25.033 --> 14:26.861
[ Groans ]

14:26.931 --> 14:30.551
[ Screaming ]

14:30.620 --> 14:31.793
FOR THIS DEMONSTRATION

14:31.861 --> 14:34.344
I'VE PLACED ONE OF MOTHER'S BRAS
ON IGNOR.

14:34.413 --> 14:35.654
[ Sobs ]

14:35.724 --> 14:39.413
THE ROBOT CONTROLLER IS
NESTLED HERE IN THE LEFT CUP.

14:39.481 --> 14:40.688
NEVER FEAR.

14:40.758 --> 14:43.895
MY MAGIC FINGERS STILL KNOW
HOW TO DO THEIR STUFF.

14:43.965 --> 14:45.965
[ Joints Cracking ]

14:46.033 --> 14:48.102
TO ESCAPE THE ROBOT DEATH SQUADS

14:48.172 --> 14:50.654
WE'LL TAKE MOTHER TO HER RUSTIC
CABIN IN THE BRONX.

14:50.724 --> 14:55.000
YOU CAN GET THERE
USING THIS PRECIOUS
NON-COMPUTERIZED MAP.

14:55.067 --> 14:56.240
LEELA BRING FIRE?

14:56.309 --> 14:57.861
NO, WE'RE SET FOR FIRE, THANKS.

14:57.931 --> 15:00.447
THE PROFESSOR CAN'T
WALK ALL THE WAY
TO THE BRONX.

15:00.517 --> 15:03.447
HOW ARE WE GOING
TO GET THERE
WITHOUT A HOVER CAR?

15:03.517 --> 15:06.895
WAIT! IN MY TIME, WE HAD A WAY
OF MOVING THINGS LONG DISTANCES
WITHOUT HOVERING.

15:06.965 --> 15:09.724
- IMPOSSIBLE.
- IT WAS CALLED... LET ME THINK.

15:09.793 --> 15:11.172
IT WAS REALLY FAMOUS.

15:11.240 --> 15:13.758
RUTH GORDON HAD ONE.
THE WHEEL!

15:13.826 --> 15:15.206
NEVER HEARD OF IT.

15:15.274 --> 15:17.102
SHOW US THIS...
THE WHEEL.

15:17.172 --> 15:20.379
[ Sawing And Hammering ]

15:20.447 --> 15:22.172
THERE, FINISHED.

15:22.240 --> 15:24.067
[ All Exclaim ]

15:24.136 --> 15:26.240
WOULDN'T IT WORK BETTER
IF THE WHEELS WERE ROUND?

15:26.309 --> 15:27.965
IT'S MY INVENTION.
WE DO IT MY WAY.

15:28.033 --> 15:30.724
NOW ALL WE NEED IS SOMETHING
TO PULL IT AND WE'RE SET.

15:30.793 --> 15:32.274
[ Grunting ]

15:32.344 --> 15:34.481
HEE-YAH!OW!

15:34.551 --> 15:37.000
HURRY!

15:37.067 --> 15:38.965
THE ROBOTS HAVE TAKEN
SUFFOLK COUNTY.

15:39.033 --> 15:40.413
I'M READY TO SEDUCE.

15:40.481 --> 15:42.654
I'M WEARING
MY KISSING DENTURES

15:42.724 --> 15:44.447
AND MY EVENING TRUSS.

15:44.517 --> 15:46.344
HERE, GIVE HER THESE.

15:46.413 --> 15:50.033
AND IF THAT DOESN'T WORK
I GOT YOU A SIX-PACK
OF CHAMPAGNE AND A FUNNEL.

15:53.481 --> 15:55.931
WHO THE SWEATY HELL IS IT?

15:56.000 --> 15:58.481
[ Gasps ]
HUBERT FARNSWORTH?

15:59.481 --> 16:01.172
I WAS OUT FLEEING
SOME ROBOTS

16:01.240 --> 16:03.274
AND THE SILVERY
MOONLIGHT GLINTING

16:03.344 --> 16:06.067
OFF THEIR BLOODY CLAWS
MADE ME THINK OF YOU.

16:06.136 --> 16:08.206
IT'S BEEN
A LONG TIME

16:08.274 --> 16:12.481
YOU PUS-DRIPPING SACK
OF DOUBLE-SMOKED BUTT JERKY.

16:12.551 --> 16:14.309
UH-HUH. MAY I COME IN?

16:14.379 --> 16:16.379
NEVER!

16:16.447 --> 16:18.654
OOH! AH! OH! EW! AH!

16:18.724 --> 16:22.931
IS THIS WHAT HUMAN
MATING LOOKS LIKE?

16:23.000 --> 16:24.654
BECAUSE I LIKE IT.

16:24.724 --> 16:26.793
MOVE YOUR FREAKING HOOF,
YOU GOAT!

16:26.861 --> 16:28.965
HERE, I BROUGHT YOU THESE.

16:29.033 --> 16:31.654
OH, WHY, DAFFODILS.

16:31.724 --> 16:34.895
70 YEARS AND YOU REMEMBERED
MY FAVORITE FLOWER.

16:34.965 --> 16:36.206
YOUR FAVORITE WHAT?

16:36.274 --> 16:37.895
WHY DOES MY FOOT HURT?

16:37.965 --> 16:39.206
WON'T YOU COME IN?

16:40.274 --> 16:42.033
YES!

16:42.102 --> 16:44.724
YOU BROKE MY
HEART, HUBERT.

16:44.793 --> 16:46.206
AND YOU BROKE MINE.

16:46.274 --> 16:49.688
GRANTED, THAT WAS
FOUR OR FIVE HEARTS AGO.

16:49.758 --> 16:52.067
SO, WHAT HAVE YOU
BEEN UP TO
ALL THESE YEARS?

16:52.136 --> 16:55.793
OH, INVENTING.
SENDING DELIVERY CREWS
TO THEIR DOOM

16:55.861 --> 16:57.793
BREEDING ATOMIC MONSTERS.

16:57.861 --> 16:59.102
HONESTLY, HUBERT.

16:59.172 --> 17:01.688
YOU AND YOUR ATOMIC MONSTERS.

17:01.758 --> 17:02.965
[ Both Chuckling ]

17:12.309 --> 17:13.964
YOUR EYES ALWAYS WERE

17:14.034 --> 17:17.240
THE MOST BEAUTIFUL
SHADE OF MILKY WHITE.

17:17.309 --> 17:21.964
AND YOUR SKIN STILL DANGLES
SO GRACEFULLY FROM YOUR NECK.

17:22.034 --> 17:22.964
DARLING, HUBIE

17:23.034 --> 17:25.136
I SHOULD NEVER
HAVE TRIED TO TAMPER

17:25.205 --> 17:27.550
WITH THAT CUTE LITTLE
Q.T. McWHISKERS.

17:27.619 --> 17:30.103
NO, IT WAS SILLY
OF ME TO OBJECT.

17:30.172 --> 17:32.931
ONE FOOT TALL,
EIGHT FEET, FIFTEEN FEET--

17:33.000 --> 17:34.586
WHAT DOES IT MATTER?

17:34.654 --> 17:37.172
YOU SHOULD SEE THE
NEW 16-FOOT MODELS.

17:37.240 --> 17:39.205
16 FEET?!
GO TO HELL!

17:39.275 --> 17:42.689
I WAS A FOOL TO THINK
YOU'D CHANGED, YOU OLD BAT.

17:42.758 --> 17:45.103
FILTHY, TOOTHLESS
NERD BASTARD!

17:45.172 --> 17:47.172
DAMNED SHE-FOSSIL!

17:47.240 --> 17:48.689
STINK PIG!

17:48.758 --> 17:51.067
[ Both Moaning ]

17:57.723 --> 17:58.964
HERE WE GO.

17:59.034 --> 18:01.413
JUST UNHOOK IT
AND GET THE REMOTE.

18:01.481 --> 18:05.000
SO MANY HOOKS.
COME ON, FARNSWORTH.

18:05.067 --> 18:07.067
DRAT! THE FIRST ONE'S BACK ON AGAIN!

18:07.136 --> 18:08.481
I GIVE UP.

18:08.550 --> 18:10.758
WAIT! VICTORY!

18:12.481 --> 18:13.413
OH, MY.

18:13.481 --> 18:16.413
NOW I'LL JUST...
THE REMOTE.

18:16.481 --> 18:17.862
I'LL JUST...

18:17.931 --> 18:19.309
OH, MY.

18:22.172 --> 18:23.654
[ Both Moaning ]

18:27.034 --> 18:28.136
I'M WORRIED.

18:28.205 --> 18:30.413
IT SHOULDN'T TAKE
THIS LONG TO GET
TO SECOND BASE.

18:30.481 --> 18:32.619
[ Yelling ]

18:32.689 --> 18:33.758
LAND ROBOTS!

18:33.826 --> 18:37.275
I'VE GOT A BIG, BIG THIRST
FOR HUMAN BLOOD!

18:37.344 --> 18:39.172
[ All Screaming ]

18:41.344 --> 18:44.619
WHERE IN FUNKY TOWN
IS THE PROFESSOR?!

18:44.689 --> 18:47.034
NOTHING IN HERE BUT A COUPLE
OF ELEPHANT-SKIN RUGS.

18:47.103 --> 18:48.172
[ Gasps ]

18:48.240 --> 18:50.136
[ All Gasping ]

18:56.067 --> 18:58.517
- OH, YES.
- [ Banging ]

18:58.586 --> 19:00.792
[ Robots ]
THEY'RE INSIDE! GET THEM!

19:00.862 --> 19:03.654
I SUPPOSE I SHOULD
SWITCH OFF THE ROBOTS

19:03.723 --> 19:07.205
BEFORE THEY RUIN
THIS WONDERFUL ROMANTIC EVENING.

19:07.275 --> 19:10.000
EVERYONE, HELP MOM
FIND HER BRA.

19:14.103 --> 19:15.654
EW!

19:15.723 --> 19:18.378
[ Grunting ]

19:18.448 --> 19:20.378
THERE IT IS.

19:20.448 --> 19:23.378
[ Chuckling ]

19:23.448 --> 19:25.826
FAN BEATS MAN!

19:25.895 --> 19:27.586
IS ANYTHING NOT A ROBOT?

19:27.654 --> 19:29.172
I'M NOT A ROBOT.

19:31.275 --> 19:34.309
[ Coughs ]
ALL RIGHT, GREETING CARD,
I'LL GRAB THE CASH

19:34.378 --> 19:36.240
YOU WRECK UP THE PLACE
AND... HUH?!

19:36.309 --> 19:37.586
YOU! BENDING UNIT!

19:37.654 --> 19:40.448
MOMMY NEEDS THAT BRA
TO END THE ROBOT REBELLION.

19:40.517 --> 19:41.862
STRETCH UP AND GET IT FOR ME.

19:41.931 --> 19:44.309
SORRY, MA,
BUT YOU ORDERED ME TO REBEL

19:44.378 --> 19:45.862
AND LOOT I SHALL.

19:45.931 --> 19:47.758
OOH, A SIX-PACK
OF STRAWBERRY CHAMPAGNE.

19:47.826 --> 19:49.136
DON'T MIND
IF I HELP MYSELF.

19:49.205 --> 19:50.689
No, comrade Bender.

19:50.758 --> 19:53.067
Liquor is the opiate
of the human bourgeoisie.

19:53.136 --> 19:56.654
SAY WHAT?In the glorious robot
workers' paradise

19:56.723 --> 20:00.240
there will be no liquor,
only efficient synthetic fuels.

20:00.309 --> 20:04.378
NO LIQUOR?!
DOSVEDANYA,COMRADE!

20:04.448 --> 20:07.586
NO! [ Melody Plays, Slows Down, Stops ]

20:07.654 --> 20:09.723
[ Banging ]

20:09.792 --> 20:12.378
HURRY, BENDER,
GET THE BRA!

20:12.448 --> 20:14.654
OKAY, FAN, JUST HOLD STILL
AND LET ME...

20:14.723 --> 20:17.344
HEY! WHOA!

20:20.172 --> 20:22.481
[ All Scream ]

20:22.550 --> 20:24.413
DEATH TO ALL HUMANS!

20:29.792 --> 20:32.413
FREE SODA FOR ALL HUMANS!

20:32.481 --> 20:34.517
[ All Cheer ]

20:37.931 --> 20:39.275
I LOVE YOU, MOM.

20:39.344 --> 20:41.792
LET'S GROW
ANCIENT TOGETHER.

20:41.862 --> 20:44.413
WAY TO GO, PROFESSOR.
THE PLAN WORKED.

20:44.481 --> 20:46.862
"PLAN"? WHAT PLAN?

20:46.931 --> 20:51.172
I THOUGHT THIS WAS
A SPONTANEOUS WHIRLWIND
OF HOT, DRY SEX.

20:51.240 --> 20:53.792
LOOK, IT STARTED OUT
AS A CALCULATED PLOT

20:53.862 --> 20:56.240
TO RUMMAGE THROUGH
YOUR UNDERWEAR

20:56.309 --> 20:59.654
BUT ONCE I GOT IN THERE,
I FOUND MORE. MUCH MORE!

20:59.723 --> 21:02.931
AND NOW I WANT
TO SHOUT OUR LOVE
FROM THE ROOFTOPS.

21:03.000 --> 21:05.413
PERHAPS I'LL BREED
SOME SORT OF ALBINO

21:05.481 --> 21:07.000
SHOUTING GORILLA THAT--

21:07.067 --> 21:09.654
GET OUT OF MY HOUSE,
YOU LYING SCUM PILE!

21:09.723 --> 21:11.619
I NEVER WANT
TO SEE YOU AGAIN!

21:11.689 --> 21:13.895
BUT, DUSTCAKES...

21:15.205 --> 21:16.826
OH...

21:29.586 --> 21:33.792
WELL, TIME FOR THIS ROBOT
TO GET BACK TO WORK.

21:33.862 --> 21:35.344
AH...

21:35.413 --> 21:39.034
TOO BAD IT DIDN'T WORK OUT
WITH MOM, PROFESSOR.

21:39.103 --> 21:41.309
YES, BUT I'LL
ALWAYS LOVE HER

21:41.378 --> 21:43.344
IN MY OWN SUBTLE WAY.

21:44.758 --> 21:47.034
LOVE MOM!

21:47.103 --> 21:48.758
LOVE MOM!

21:48.826 --> 21:50.344
LOVE MOM!

21:50.413 --> 21:51.964
LOVE MOM!

21:52.034 --> 21:54.895
MOM! MOM! MOM!

21:57.862 --> 22:01.309
[ Child's Voice ]
You created me, Mom,
so I guess you're to blame

22:01.378 --> 22:05.240
for the love that I feel
just from hearing your name

22:05.309 --> 22:09.654
you're as tender as corned beef
and warm as pastrami--

22:09.723 --> 22:13.964
[ Chiming Tones ]
I wuvmy mommy.
